<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١١٥٩٤ -<span class="c5"> عَنِ الثَّوْرِيِّ قَالَ:</span> كَانَ الْحَسَنُ: <span class="c2">«لَا يَرَى ظِهَارَهَا مِنْ زَوْجِهَا ظِهَارًا»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>